__note_speed: Fast speed means it will speed up at the position that is unlikely to make you stuck, also dont set speed to high or you might still get stuck due to game anticheat or gold node havent even respawn yet
__note_stuck: STUCK_TIME_REQUIRED means if ur position doesnt change in 15sec it will considered stuck and will try to unstuck
__note_webhook: WEBHOOK_URL will post the start and finished msg STUCK_WEBHOOK_URL will post only the stuck msg
__note_goldlimit: GOLD_LIMIT means it will scan your inv for how much gold you have so it can decide whether to send finish msg and stop picking up or not
